了。</blockquote><br />\n咁叫AA咪得 點解要加個制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n實行呢個制度囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6ad8cb6c92bf5e54560eaa997f580845bd550d","tid":219301,"uid":69130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:15:49.000Z","msg":"因為你叫啲女比錢 佢地會 A A 聲，好似禁左制咁"},{"pid":"9a1ca009087fa19eadc0ccc98bcb07b40ce96a91","tid":219301,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:56:09.000Z","msg":"好詳細， 咁即係外國人唔會咁叫？我見通過都係話split the bill"},{"pid":"c8fbf38e753f5f874e9af16acf2da4b4c5e7a39c","tid":219301,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:58:20.000Z","msg":"a for apple"},{"pid":"b6cc5f446fb284d83183bb07624541e3c678989e","tid":219301,"uid":70538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:11:53.000Z","msg":"let's go dutch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60eda6d4a73b870b06df2b1e4912c8869d31fc33","tid":219301,"uid":54451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:12:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為你叫啲女比錢 佢地會 A A 聲，好似禁左制咁</blockquote><br />\n㩒 掣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8798503d1a101f7a60a48bc4a93e369f197559","tid":219301,"uid":17496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:15:40.000Z","msg":"對aa cup 港女就要AA 制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edefa74b99094e13a0715c70da1f2baf9b9c6eab","tid":219301,"uid":75898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:56:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好詳細， 咁即係外國人唔會咁叫？我見通過都係話split the bill</blockquote><br />\n以前會叫go Dutch, 好似係因為笑鳩d荷蘭人窮, 唔肯請客 淨係岀自己個份"}]}